sequenceDiagram
    actor Visitor
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Visitor->>Frontend: Fill registration form
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/register
    API->>API: Validate payload
    API->>DB: Check email uniqueness

    alt Email available
        DB-->>API: Email not used
        API->>API: Hash password
        API->>DB: Insert user
        DB-->>API: User created
        API-->>Frontend: 201 Created
        Frontend-->>Visitor: Show registration success
    else Email already used
        DB-->>API: Existing user found
        API-->>Frontend: 409 Conflict
        Frontend-->>Visitor: Display error message
    end
